        <p class="text-xl text-gray-100 leading-relaxed">
          Thank you for providing your project details. We've generated a comprehensive rough guide for your construction project.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Next Steps -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4">What Happens Next?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Here's what you can expect from Pure Logic Solutions
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-base/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üìß</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Check Your Email</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Your rough guide has been sent to your email. Download the PDF for your records.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-base/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üìû</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">We'll Reach Out</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Our team will contact you within 1-2 business days to discuss your project in detail.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-base/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üèóÔ∏è</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Schedule Consultation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            We'll schedule an on-site visit to provide an accurate, detailed quote.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Important Notice -->
      <div class="bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/20 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <div class="text-2xl">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-200 mb-2">
              Important: This is a Rough Guide, Not a Final Quote
            </h3>
            <p class="text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm">
              The estimate you received is based on industry-standard pricing and the information you provided. 
              Final costs may vary based on site conditions, material availability, specific requirements, and 
              after a detailed on-site assessment. A formal quote will be provided after our consultation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" size="lg">
          Schedule a Consultation Now
        </Button>
        <Button href="/" variant="secondary" size="lg">
          Back to Home
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg text-center mb-12">Questions About Your Estimate?</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">How accurate is this estimate?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Our calculator uses current Utah market rates and provides a realistic range. However, final costs 
            depend on many factors including specific material choices, site conditions, and project complexity. 
            We recommend treating this as a budgeting guide.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">When will I hear from you?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            We aim to contact all leads within 1-2 business days. If your timeline is urgent, 
            please call us directly at (801) 555-0123.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">What should I do to prepare?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Start gathering inspiration photos, thinking about your must-haves vs. nice-to-haves, 
            and any questions you have about the process. We'll guide you through everything during 
            our consultation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Is there an obligation to move forward?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Absolutely not. The estimate and initial consultation are free with no obligation. 
            We want you to make the best decision for your project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4">Need to Talk Sooner?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
        Don't want to wait? Give us a call or send an email anytime.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a 
          href="tel:+18015550123" 
          class="flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-base hover:text-brand-dark font-semibold"
        >
          <span class="text-2xl">üìû</span>
          (801) 555-0123
        </a>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-gray-400">|</span>
        <a 
          href="mailto:info@purelogic-solutions.com" 
          class="flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-base hover:text-brand-dark font-semibold"
        >
          <span class="text-2xl">‚úâÔ∏è</span>
